4. Competitive Differentiators (Food & Beverage)

vs. Legacy Brands
	•	Cleaner ingredients
	•	Lower sugar
	•	Transparent sourcing
	•	Functional benefits (energy, calm, digestion, hydration)

vs. Cheaper Grocery Store Brands
	•	Higher quality formulation
	•	Real ingredients vs. artificial additives
	•	Better taste
	•	Higher performance benefits

vs. Other DTC Competitors
	•	Unique flavor profiles
	•	More rigorous testing
	•	Better experience (less jittery, smoother taste, shorter ingredient label)
	•	Better value per serving

